<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>For Bebi Reana</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #ffe6f0;
    margin: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page {
    display: none;
    background: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    width: 80%;
    max-width: 600px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .active {
    display: block;
  }

  button {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
    background: #ff4d88;
    color: white;
  }

  .noBtn {
    background: #aaa;
    margin-left: 10px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- PAGE 1 -->
<div class="page active" id="p1">
  <h1>Advance Happy Birthday Bebi Reana 🎉</h1>
  <button onclick="nextPage(2)">papindot po mæm</button>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 2 -->
<div class="page" id="p2">
  <p>
    Everything started nung inasar ako ng mga cm ko sayo and grabe yung relationship na nabuo natin dahil lang sa asar,
    mas nakilala kita and that made me realize
  </p>
  <button onclick="nextPage(3)">Next</button>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 3 -->
<div class="page" id="p3">
  <p>
    I realized na you deserve to be loved and treated like a princess, nasabi ko na sa sarili ko nuon na gusto ko iparamdan
    sayo kung ano talaga ang deserve mo
  </p>
  <button onclick="nextPage(4)">Next</button>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 4 -->
<div class="page" id="p4">
  <p>
    I wanna say sorry din pala if nagkaron ng times na I can't make my decision myself dahil sa problems ko kaya it affected everything
    surrounding me including my friend and you especially my baby (yiee). You obviously did not deserve that...
    that's why sa mga oras na yun nagdoubt din ako sa sarili ko if I should keep going and God told me to keep going kasi
    this princess is gonna make me realize it and it did.
  </p>
  <button onclick="nextPage(5)">Next</button>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 5 -->
<div class="page" id="p5">
  <p>
    It's been exactly 5 months since we usap-usap ng walang label HAHA grabe noh ang bilis parang kahapon lang nagkaka-hiyaan pa tayo mag sabay sa recess
  </p>
  <button onclick="nextPage(6)">Next</button>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 6 -->
<div class="page" id="p6">
  <p>
    I know you confessed to me about your feelings a month ago and I'm super proud and shocked nung mga moments na yun
    that's why I'm super pressured to respond kasi you're so strong and I don't wanna decide unconsciously...
    uhmmmmm eto na po tatanong ko na
  </p>
  <button onclick="nextPage(7)">Next</button>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 7 (QUESTION) -->
<div class="page" id="p7">
  <h2>With a chance or not boi can I court you?</h2>
  <button onclick="yes()">Yes 💖</button>
  <button class="noBtn" onclick="no()">No 😢</button>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 8 (YES FINAL) -->
<div class="page" id="p8">
  <p>
    Thank you so much for letting me court you even na hindi pa talaga natin kilala ang isa't isa ng sobra.
    I will promise na never kong babaliin yang tiwala mo and I wanna say na I LOVE YOU SO MUCH BEBII 💖
    ADVANCE HAPPY BIRTHDAY 🎉
  </p>
</div>

<script>
  function nextPage(n) {
    document.querySelectorAll(".page").forEach(p => p.classList.remove("active"));
    document.getElementById("p" + n).classList.add("active");
  }

  function yes() {
    nextPage(8);
  }

  function no() {
    nextPage(7);
    alert("Okay... try again 😢");
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
